<HEAD>Suspects Arrested in Slaying of Crime Witness</HEAD>
<DATELINE>DENVER (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Two brothers and the girlfriend of a robbery
suspect have been arrested in connection with the June 6 slaying of
two people, one of whom was scheduled to testify against the
suspect, authorities said.
   Christopher Young, 21, and Joseph Young, 20, both brothers of
robbery suspect Roger Lee Young, were being held without bail for
investigation of first-degree murder in the shooting deaths of Frank
Magnuson and Daniel Smith, police said. Kevin Fears, 20, also was
