before he was to testify in the kidnapping and robbery trial of
28-year-old Roger Lee Young.
   Police had speculated the slayings were related to Magnuson's
testimony.
   Denver police spokesman Aristedes Zavaras said the crime could
have ``struck fear in the hearts of witnesses'' and that police had
been working non-stop for a break in the case.
