<HEAD>Gunmen Loot Seminary in South Sudan, Kidnap Seminarians</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NAIROBI, Kenya (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Unidentified gunmen looted a Roman Catholic
